See the project README for full citation details and links.

---

AI-assisted development

The software and documentation in this repository were substantially developed
with the assistance of large language models via the Cursor IDE, including
Claude Opus 4.6 and Sonnet 4.6 (Anthropic), GPT-5.4 (OpenAI), and Cursor
Composer 2. The human author directed all design decisions and takes
responsibility for the final work.

